items.name: Billions of Plants/Shrooms - Standalone
items.description:
With YAML-files you just get 1 nice wildcard-file Instead of 100 files. They are easy readable (best with Notepadd++) and they are easy to maintain.

The wildcards follow the same scheme as the Billions of Characters wildcards. You can use them together. However, this set has no dependencies within BoChars.

Don't forget to leave a ❤️ to get a notification for future updates. ⭐ reviews are appreciated, too. Let me see what you created with this tool. ;)

note: Yaml files will throw isseus when using: "a1111-sd-webui-tagcomplete"extension. That's related to the extension, not the wildcards. Update this extension to solve this issue.

Usage

Unleash the full power:

Activate: Dynamic Prompts->Advanced Options->Unlink seed from prompt

Usage is pretty much the same as for "regular" wildcards.

You need the SD Dynamic Prompt Extension. Put the files directly into the wildcard folder:

~\stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-dynamic-prompts\wildcards

They show up as a menu on the left in the Wildcards tab.

The YAML is structured and indented (that's how they work). Just with a little difference. You have to add the category layers in the wildcard.

Examples:

__BoPlants/random-plant__
__BoPlant/random-shroom__

A cool thing you can do, too, is using a wildcard "*" in the wildcards. So you could use the normal chararcter wildcards in the same prompt and get chars from both sets:

__properties/patterns/*__    # you'll get all patterns from my other sets
__properties/materials*/*__  # you'll get all materials from my other sets
__properties/colors/*__      # you'll get all colors from my other sets

I made easy to use wildcards for building and room creations.

There might be some wildcards that are not used for it. Have a look what's in there, too. You'll find a full list below. You can use each subcategory separately.

You are welcome

Leave a star review, if you like it. so other can find those awesome cards more easily.

I plan to add more themes as extensions in the future. SDXL is coming, and wildcards are limitless.

If you want to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. ;)

Have experimenting with it.

items.name: Camila Mendes (JG)
items.description:
Camila Mendes is an American actress of Brazilian descenet, mostly known for her role as Veronica Lodge in the TV show Riverdale.

120-step TI trained on a dataset of 15 images with these settings.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Do you have a specific idea for a TI in mind? Visit my website and let me know.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of beautiful (cm3nd3s:0.99), a woman with beautiful hair, hair upsweep updo, as a movie star in a (movie premiere), premiere gala, (near a movie theatre), natural skin texture, (elegant {red|yellow|blue|green|black|turquoise} sweater off-shoulder with suspenders), 24mm, 4k textures, soft cinematic light, adobe lightroom, photolab, hdr, intricate, elegant, highly detailed, sharp focus, ((((cinematic look)))), soothing tones, insane details, intricate details, hyperdetailed, low contrast, soft cinematic light, exposure blend, hdr, faded, (paparazzi in background), (painted lips:1.1), ((looking straight at the camera:1.1)), (smiling)"

items.name: Fantexi_realistic
items.description:
If you like my model please support me ko-fi

Of course, there are also some test models that have not been published in civitai, if you are interested, you can also go to download

About the model

This version is a derivative version of Fantexi _V0.8, which inherits part of the features of 0.8. In terms of face drawing, it can draw 4-6 different faces, and can provide high-definition real portraits and details at medium and short distances

known issues

  1. Hands are drawn as feet in certain poses (I haven't found a solution yet, if anyone knows how to solve it please let me know, thanks a lot)

  2. Hands and feet will be drawn unclearly at long distances

How to solve problem

  • Use After Detailer to fix distant hands, feet and faces

  • Only draw the body part above the feet

  • Use ControlNet to help generate the correct pose，Use inpainting combined with depth map to repair deformed hands and feet

civital cannot fill in the complete picture parameters, please download my sample picture and drag it into the picture browser of sd to view the parameters

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description:
If you like my model ，please support me on Ko-fi，Of course, there are also some test models that have not yet been released, if you are interested, you can go to download

This model is a real version of the model adapted to Fantexi_V0.8, inheriting part of the original version of the face, randomly can draw 4 - 6 different faces, prompts and parameters can refer to the example picture，The model produces good results in terms of near and medium distances

Known problem：

  1. Hands are drawn as feet when doing certain poses (if any of you know how to solve this problem, please let me know, thank you very much)

  2. Feet and hands are not well drawn at a distance

  3. Deformities of hands and feet are less likely, and feet are more frequent

How to solve it：

  1. Use After Detailer toRepair hands and feet and face from a distance

  2. Do not open Hires. fix, run multiple pictures at once, view samples of correct human structure from thumbnails, copy seeds for Hires. fix

  3. Use ControlNet the new version of DW Pose can detect hands and body more perfectly, and can control posture more precisely

  4. Use ControlNet Depth map control to fix wrong hands and feet by redrawing layer masks

  5. Keep the characters from showing their feet

  6. Draw the part that does not contain feet by tag

items.description:
Who is she? The hard working scientist? The doctor working ER. The mall worker waiting for her shift to end? She's no-one who exists, but is here as an embedding.

I recommend you use ADetailer to show it at its best.

This uses the same method I describe here, but with my more recent lessons in doing embeddings. I found a face I liked in Stable Diffusion then used Faceapp to map it onto a set of faces, and then used that to train an embedding.

This one came from a character in my Big City Girls story on Deviant art (muscle growth, boob growth - though the embedding is her as a normal woman). After it worked on Meryl, I thought I should use Xia too, as she's one of the major characters in the Big City Girls stories - and "not beautiful" is one of the harder things to get Stable Diffusion to do.

items.description:
国画千里江山图

千里江山图，北宋18岁天才，王希孟的旷世之作，是中国历史上一幅极具代表性的画作。该作品以长卷形式，立足传统，画面细致入微，烟波浩渺的江河、层峦起伏的群山构成了一幅美妙的江南山水图，渔村野市、水榭亭台、茅庵草舍、水磨长桥等静景穿插捕鱼、驶船、游玩、赶集等动景，动静结合恰到好处。

v2 XL 更新

此次更新，重新挑选了画面素材，补充了更多的细节内容，极致的还原画面的景色。

实践

Lora值：0.6~0.8

触发词：SongQiLi

相关的提示词：mountain，waterfall，rock，boat，river，tree，chinese style

尺寸：1024x2048, 2048x1024, 2048x2048，都可以直接出。

基础模型：SDXL 1.0

另外加了自己训练的人脸模型【未发布】，道友们可以自己选择其他人脸模型；

一些demo，喜欢千里的朋友可以入座细品。

============================================================

Chinese Painting | A Thousand Miles of Rivers and Mountains

"A Thousand Miles of Rivers and Mountains" is a masterpiece by Wang Ximeng, an 18-year-old prodigy of the Northern Song dynasty. It is an extraordinarily representative artwork in Chinese history. Presented in the form of a long scroll, the painting adheres to tradition, displaying intricate details. The vast rivers shrouded in mist and the undulating mountain ranges compose a magnificent landscape of Jiangnan. Tranquil scenes such as fishing villages, riverside markets, elegant pavilions, thatched cottages, and a long bridge over a watermill are interspersed with dynamic depictions of fishing, boating, leisure activities, and bustling gatherings, creating a harmonious blend of stillness and motion.

Model Introduction

Inspired by the Chinese painting "A Thousand Miles of Rivers and Mountains," I selected unique scenes from the artwork. After training this model, I hope fellow enthusiasts will appreciate it! I am on a journey of alchemical exploration, with rudimentary skills and ongoing discoveries. I eagerly welcome guidance from fellow practitioners.

I hold deep affection for this work, hence this idea. I invite you all to take a seat, offer corrections and comments, and engage in a learning exchange.

Looking forward to fellow practitioners sharing their insights and creations!!!

============================================================

v2 XL Update

In this update, a new selection of visual materials has been made, incorporating more intricate details to meticulously recreate the scenery of the artwork.

Practice

Lora Value: 0.6~0.8

Trigger Word: SongQiLi

Relevant Prompts: mountain, waterfall, rock, boat, river, tree, Chinese style

Size: 1024x2048, 2048x1024, 2048x2048, all available for direct output.

Base Model: SDXL 1.0

Additionally, a self-trained facial model has been added [not yet released], fellow practitioners can choose other facial models at their own discretion.

Several demos are provided; those who admire "A Thousand Miles" are invited to take a seat and savor.

END.
